Package: ContextLinkr
Title: Link Individual-Level Records to Geographic Contextual Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Todd", "Burus", email = "tburus@uky.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for geocoding location data, identifying geographic
    units, linking individual-level records to geographic identifiers, and
    joining user-supplied contextual variables for multilevel health research.
